{"tid":2362780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油站職員稱屢遭印度教友人滋擾 向印度廟掟生豬肉報復 被判感化15個月","createTime":"2021-01-11T16:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:47:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"16d34c0cd5bc0f83288262ebb82b2e2508622232","tid":2362780,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"油站職員聲稱因不忿其信奉印度教的友人經常來電滋擾，遂於去年向跑馬地一間印度廟的神像投擲生肉。職員早前承認作出有違公德的行為罪，今在東區裁判法院被判接受15個月感化令。暫委裁判官陳志輝判刑指，即使不滿意對方的行為，亦不可影響他人的宗教。<br />\n<br />\n陳官今指，早前法庭為被告索取的感化官報告內容正面，從中感到被告的深切悔意，因此法庭願意接受感化官的判刑建議，惟被告須遵守三項條件，包括接受心理及精神治療課程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/IDNTQOJLFNEMDIKV4ZIRURAP3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2FIDNTQOJLFNEMDIKV4ZIRURAP3E%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=af63d678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2FIDNTQOJLFNEMDIKV4ZIRURAP3E%2F&h=c5da07bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/IDNTQOJLFNEMDIKV4ZIRURAP3E/</a>"},{"pid":"439c7051cfee069ad860d23c443e28c710a12390","tid":2362780,"uid":84123,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"識玩<br />\n一陣比真主燒撚死"},{"pid":"552a00bb99dc46a9d35a739a05f4f5ddb4b587f8","tid":2362780,"uid":85461,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T21:43:15.000Z","msg":"印度廟掉咩豬肉呀<br />\n印度係牛肉呀 牛係神聖<br />\n伊斯蘭係豬肉 豬係不潔"},{"pid":"288341ca65240b539607b550d6d7653e4c3097af","tid":2362780,"uid":22692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T21:52:11.000Z","msg":"好鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e894f403dae08ad05dd26074